 borides. Our study\nillustrates the inverse correlation between the thermodynamic stability and\nsuperconducting properties and the necessity to carefully examine both in the\ndesign of new synthesizable superconducting materials.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 11 Jul 2013 18:49:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-16"}
