 A_0\ncan also be determined quite accurately. For comparable computational effort\nthe \\chi^2 minimization yielded much worse results.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 12 Jul 2013 09:13:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 19 Jul 2013 15:12:04 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 9 Oct 2013 11:42:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-10-30"}
