ding VHE\ndetection prospects for observations of GRB-like transient events with\nCherenkov telescopes. In particular, we consider the observation of the\ntransient event GRB 090102 as a test case for the method and show the achieved\ndetection prospects under different observational conditions for the MAGIC\ntelescopes and CTA.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 12 Jul 2013 13:25:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-07-15"}
